==概要==
2008年9月4日, [[Honda|Honda]] 公佈了Insight 二代新車型為五門[[油電車|油電車]]。<ref name="AB2ndGen">{{cite web |url=http://www.autoblog.com/2008/09/04/paris-preview-officially-official-hondas-new-hybrid-is-the-in/ |title="Paris Preview: Officially Official, Honda's new hybrid is the Insight!" |accessdate=2008-09-04 |last=Abuelsamid |first=Sam |date=2008-09-04 |format=HTML |work=[[Autoblog|Autoblog]] |publisher=[[Weblogs,_Inc.|Weblogs, Inc.]] |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029055449/https://www.autoblog.com/2008/09/04/paris-preview-officially-official-hondas-new-hybrid-is-the-in/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 概念車於2008[[巴黎車展|巴黎車展]]亮相。<ref>{{cite web |last=Cunningham |first=Wayne |title="New Honda Insight no Prius-killer" |work="CNet" |url=http://reviews.cnet.com/8301-13746_7-10056658-48.html |accessdate=2008-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081005074032/http://reviews.cnet.com/8301-13746_7-10056658-48.html |archive-date=2008-10-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.leftlanenews.com/honda-insight.html |title="Full reveal: 2010 Honda Insight Concept" |date=2008-10-02 |work="Left Lane News" |accessdate=2009-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100109093911/http://www.leftlanenews.com/honda-insight.html |archive-date=2010-01-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>北美則在[[洛杉磯車展|洛杉磯車展]]亮相。<ref name="automobiles.honda.com">{{cite web|last=Walton |first=William III |title=Insight Concept Makes Its North American Debut at the L.A. Auto Show |work=automobiles.honda.com |date=2008-11-19 |url=http://automobiles.honda.com/insight-hybrid/blogdetail.aspx?id=34 |accessdate=2009-01-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090117065201/http://automobiles.honda.com/insight-hybrid/blogdetail.aspx?id=34 |archivedate=2009-01-17 }}</ref>

新一代以駕駛者習慣為基礎的燃油科技命名為「節能駕駛輔助系統」（Ecological Drive Assist System），首次用於 Honda Insight。<ref>{{cite web |title=2010 Honda Insight Hybrid Makes World Debut at the North American International Auto Show |work=automobiles.honda.com |date=2009-01-09 |url=http://automobiles.honda.com/insight-hybrid/events.aspx |accessdate=2009-01-11 |archive-date=2009-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090206232914/http://automobiles.honda.com/insight-hybrid/events.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

估計EPA（[[美國國家環境保護局|美國國家環境保護局]]）測試法測出來的油耗經濟效率是每100公里5.739升, 市區每100公里5.88升 高速公路為每100公里5.47升。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hondanews.com/categories/804/releases/4906 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-05-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090416051232/http://hondanews.com/categories/804/releases/4906 |archivedate=2009-04-16 }}</ref> <ref name="energy.gov">{{Cite web |url=http://apps1.eere.energy.gov/news/news_detail.cfm/news_id=12375 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2009-05-18 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303202857/http://apps1.eere.energy.gov/news/news_detail.cfm/news_id=12375 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
[[英國|英國]]公佈的測試為100公里3.663升，以及CO2排放101g/km, 幾乎是全英國最低。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.honda.co.uk/cars/new/jazz-hybrid/overview.html.html|title=Honda Jazz Hybrid & Jazz Crosstar - Hybrid Car - Honda UK|website=www.honda.co.uk|access-date=2020-10-08|archive-date=2020-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013071704/https://www.honda.co.uk/cars/new/jazz-hybrid/overview.html.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Honda 估計全球每年可以賣出200,000 輛，包含[[美國|美國]]區賣出的100,000 輛。 Honda還預估其他型的油電車（例如[[跑車|跑車]]型）還有一年500,000 輛的潛在市場可以在下一個10年開發出來。<ref>Murphy, John, and Kate Linebaugh. "Honda's Hybrid Will Take On Toyota Prius." Wall Street Journal 1 Oct. 2008: B1+.</ref>  2009年4月, Insight 成為第一輛在日本打敗汽油車奪下銷售冠軍的油電車。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-honda-insight-idUSTRE54A08I20090511|title=Honda Insight first hybrid to rank top in Japan|first=Reuters|last=Staff|date=2009-05-11|publisher=|via=www.reuters.com|access-date=2020-10-08|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010130128/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-honda-insight-idUSTRE54A08I20090511|dead-url=no}}</ref> 雖然洞察者的外型和價錢有優勢，但是[[馬力|馬力]]和舒適度比其他高價油電車有所犧牲。然而在[[金融海嘯|金融海嘯]]的大環境下，事實證明物美價廉比其他因素更能吸引消費者。<ref>"Honda Insight - What the Auto Press Says" http://usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/cars-trucks/Honda_Insight/ {{Wayback|url=http://usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/cars-trucks/Honda_Insight/ |date=20161027083727 }}</ref>

2012年款Insight在2011年9月[[法蘭克福車展|法蘭克福車展]]亮相。針對空氣力學改進，包括車頭水箱護罩和保桿進氣壩，車尾後保桿兩側新增一道趨近直角的折線下往後輪孔。車尾部份，更扁平的擾流尾翼，體積縮小的後擋雨刷馬達，增進車輛後方的視野面積。動力系統的效能改善：降低引擎內部阻力、CTV變速系統效能、空調系統能源管理，使二氧化碳排放量得以降低至96 g/km。除整體動力效能進步外，車室內部，改善後座座椅造型為乘員提供更佳的乘坐舒適度，而車室也加強隔音物料，令駕駛舒適性、行車穩定性、以至乘坐質感均一併提升。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.u-car.com.tw/article/14727|title=油耗排放俱進，2012年式Honda Insight法蘭克福登場|website=U-CAR.com.tw|access-date=2020-10-08|archive-date=2019-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216154809/https://news.u-car.com.tw/article/14727|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=12Insight>{{cite web|url=https://news.u-car.com.tw/article/14957|title=1.5升動力加入，日規小改Honda Insight正式曝光|website=U-CAR.com.tw|access-date=2020-10-08|archive-date=2018-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181023081542/https://news.u-car.com.tw/article/14957|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.u-car.com.tw/article/15735|title=微整型更年輕，小改Honda Insight Hybrid 1.3試駕體驗|website=U-CAR.com.tw|access-date=2020-10-08|archive-date=2020-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201012071613/https://news.u-car.com.tw/article/15735|dead-url=no}}</ref>依日本10・15油耗測試，油耗可達到31.0 km/L，而依日本{{link-ja|JC08模式|JC08モード}}測試，油耗亦達27.2 km/L。<ref name=12Insight/>

在日本市場，本田加入Insight Exclusive車系，搭配與CR-Z同樣的1.5升i-VTEC引擎與IMA系統，並配具換檔撥片的模擬7速CVT變速系統。以日本10・15油耗測試，仍可達26.5 km/L，而依日本{{link-ja|JC08模式|JC08モード}}測試，油耗亦有23.2 km/L的成績。<ref name=12Insight/>

2012年下半年，[[東風本田|東風本田]]引入中國市場。

