==售價==
本田新洞察者首度開賣地為日本, 2009年推廣到全球。[[英國|英國]]售價為£15,490英鎊. 是全世界最便宜油電車，並迅速於2009年4月成為日本新車銷售冠軍，也是第一台打敗汽油車銷售量的油電車。

2009年2月6日新洞察者於日本開賣，售價為¥1,890,000和¥2,210,000。2009年3月24日新洞察者於北美開賣，<ref>{{cite web |last=Chang |first=Richard S. |title=Honda Unveils a New Hybrid |work=The New York Times |date=2008-09-11 |url=http://wheels.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/09/11/honda-unveils-a-hybrid/ |accessdate=2009-01-11 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109104849/https://wheels.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/09/11/honda-unveils-a-hybrid/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 售價為US$19,800 和 US$ 23,200，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=2f6a9850-090a-11eb-bb82-2de2e20a7e81&url=L2FwcHMvbmV3cz9waWQ9MjA2MDExMDEmc2lkPWFRaU9RUFdudWlsOCZyZWZlcj1qYXBhbg==|title=Bloomberg - Are you a robot?|website=www.bloomberg.com}}</ref><ref>"The New Honda Insight" Hybrid Cars. 1 Oct. 2008 <{{cite web |url=http://www.hybridcars.com/compacts-sedans/honda-insight-overview.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2008-10-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081007091338/http://www.hybridcars.com/compacts-sedans/honda-insight-overview.html |archivedate=2008-10-07 }}>.</ref><ref name="ac_20080904">{{cite news |title=New Honda Insight |date=2008-09-04 |publisher=Haymarket Media Group |work=Autocar magazine |url=http://www.autocar.co.uk/News/NewsArticle/Honda-Concepts/234832/ |accessdate=2008-10-09 |archive-date=2012-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120212233926/http://www.autocar.co.uk/News/NewsArticle/Honda-Concepts/234832/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 目前也是美國最便宜的油電車。 <ref name="energy.gov"/>

於2010年12月24日在台灣上市，為當地首款進口油電車售價低於一百萬新台幣，由台灣本田股份有限公司進口。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.u-car.com.tw/article/13493|title=國內首款百萬以下Hybird車款，全新Insight 99.9萬正式開賣|website=U-CAR.com.tw|access-date=2020-10-08|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009102055/https://news.u-car.com.tw/article/13493|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.honda-taiwan.com.tw/about_news_taiwan_detail.aspx?ID=73&TN=TN |title=Honda INSIGHT Hybrid 12月24日正式上市 |access-date=2012-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110116052524/http://www.honda-taiwan.com.tw/about_news_taiwan_detail.aspx?ID=73&TN=TN |archive-date=2011-01-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

